### 事项活动记录管理接口

@baseUrl = http://localhost

### 创建事项活动记录管理
POST {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue-activity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issueId": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "action": "create",
  "field": "status",
  "oldValue": "todo",
  "newValue": "in_progress"
}

### 更新事项活动记录管理
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue-activity/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "update",
  "field": "priority"
}

### 删除事项活动记录管理
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue-activity/1

### 根据ID查询事项活动记录管理
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue-activity/1

### 查询事项活动记录管理列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue-activity/list

### 分页查询事项活动记录管理
POST {{baseUrl}}/workspace/issue-activity/page
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "issueId": null,
  "activityType": "",
  "userId": null,
  "keyword": ""
}

